items.title: Everyday Beauty: Learn How to Apply The Makeup You Own!
items.headline: Do you currently own tons of beauty products that you don't know how to use?  If yes, this course was made for you!
objectives_summary: Students will have the ability to identify the key makeup products and tools within their own makeup bag that are necessary to create a look that fits their everyday lifestyle.

Students will be able to navigate their own makeup collection to create looks that fit their everyday life by using specific guidelines when selecting color for their skin tone as it relates to eye shadow, lipstick, and blush.
Students will be able to identify key foundation and concealer types and will be able to choose the right type for their specific lifestyle.
